</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 overlooks the nearby village of La Grave, a mountaineering centre and ski resort, well-known for 
<REF ID="323.3" SEMCAT="mountain" SYNCAT="subj-det">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="pronoun" CASE="genitive">its</REFEX>
